            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Small update - I'd opened https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/37742 but after some discussion at https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/37972#issuecomment-3970233139, figured it would be better to split `gen_help_html.lua` into:\n1. turn a help page into a JSON representation of its LanguageTree object\n2. convert the JSON file into HTML\n\nThat would make it easy to add output formats (such as PDF) without risks of messing up existing ones.",
